        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 2. Boreoacanthomysis schrencki (Czerniavsky, 1882) comb. nov.: NSMT-Cr 15111, male (9.1 mm). (A) Maxilla, posterior surface; (B) endopod of first thoracic limb, posterior surface; (C) endopod of second thoracic limb, posterior surface; (D) endopod of sixth thoracic limb, posterior surface; (E) eighth thoracic limb, posterior surface; (F) penis, lateral." ;
